{
  "texts": [
    "Ensembling mitigates uncertainties associated with individual models by computing the variance of predictions across the ensemble 168.",
    "To address issues like equifinality, uncertainty, and conditional bias in predictive mapping, ensemble modeling and bias correction frameworks were proposed.",
    "Using the XGBoost model and environmental covariates, ensemble modeling resolved equifinality and improved performance 169.",
    "A comparison of regional and global ensemble models for soil mapping showed that regional ensembles had less uncertainty despite similar performance to global models 170.",
    "In this review, we highlight the multifaceted challenges encountered in geospatial data-driven modeling."
  ]
}